{"tid":2132894,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"新研究：吃泡菜可降低35%新冠肺炎死亡風險 發酵食品有益生菌／抗氧化","createTime":"2020-07-30T16:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T01:32:01.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e09f044fee2e8a1069478f390b4dcdfec2619177","tid":2132894,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"新研究：吃泡菜可降低35%新冠肺炎死亡風險 發酵食品有益生菌／抗氧化<br />\n文: Miranda Chan  發佈: 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n&quot;法國研究人員Jean Bousquet表示若國民常吃醃製、發酵蔬菜，國家新冠肺炎死亡率普遍較低。每增加1克國家的平均發酵蔬菜攝取量（克/日），國民死於新冠肺炎的風險降低35.4%。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;因為發酵食品具有抗氧化的功效，可以激活抗氧化物質Nrf2，食物中也有益生菌，有助維持腸道微生物群的健康，因此有助對抗新冠病毒。但研究顯示其他發酵食物，如牛奶、乳酪、酸奶，並未有這種功效。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/restaurant/news/detail/2707892/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%96%B0%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E5%90%83%E6%B3%A1%E8%8F%9C%E5%8F%AF%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E35-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%99%BC%E9%85%B5%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%8A%E7%94%9F%E8%8F%8C-%E6%8A%97%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Frestaurant%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2707892%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E5%2590%2583%25E6%25B3%25A1%25E8%258F%259C%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BD%258E35-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2585%25B5%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2593%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259B%258A%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%258F%258C-%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%25B0%25A7%25E5%258C%2596&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=80b6bdd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/restaurant/news/detail/2707892/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%96%B0%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E5%90%83%E6%B3%A1%E8%8F%9C%E5%8F%AF%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E35-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%